data.custrecord_knz_master_record_checklist:
Tasks for 22/10/24
  • Moved KPI types & settings tab to the first position in KPI Tile settings.
  • Added method fields with a dropdown selection for Records, Queries, Hooks, Workbooks, and Saved Searches.
  • Added fields conditionally based on the selected dropdown option.
Tasks for 23/10/24
﻿﻿﻿﻿
  • Completed the backward icon functionality, allowing the display of parent data when the icon is clicked, and updated the children data accordingly.
  • Integrated the following APIs with conditional logic to display fields and data:
  • g/ab/dashboard/primary_records
  • g/ab/dashboard/primary_records_fields
  • g/ab/dashboard/graph_preview
  • Added a "Result" button and implemented logic to change the button color on mouse hover.
  • Worked on displaying graph data using the new API functionality.
Tasks for 24/10/24
  • Displayed all real-time data in all Apache ECharts graphs.
  • Enabled real-time data display in expanded chart and table functionality.
  • Created a data format for non-functional charts.
  • Fixed the double pop issue.
  • Resolved bubble chart issue.
Tasks for 25/10/24
  • Resolved the KPI edit tile drawer issue.
  • Added modal notifications for Add Tile, Edit Tile, Clone Tile, and Delete Tile actions.
  • Fixed UI issue to display the loader in the center.
  • Completed API integration for global configuration settings.
  • Conducted developer-level testing and bug fixing.
Tasks for 29/10/24
  • Integrated API for default page settings and implemented conditional logic to display the default set page.
  • Completed the integration of the delete page API.
  • Added new fields and UI for stacked charts within all chart types.

data.title: Dashboard Customization & Filters
data.name: Dashboard Customization & Filters
data.custrecord_knz_master_record_checklist:
Tasks for 22/10/24
  • Moved KPI types & settings tab to the first position in KPI Tile settings.
  • Added method fields with a dropdown selection for Records, Queries, Hooks, Workbooks, and Saved Searches.
  • Added fields conditionally based on the selected dropdown option.
Tasks for 23/10/24
﻿﻿﻿﻿
  • Completed the backward icon functionality, allowing the display of parent data when the icon is clicked, and updated the children data accordingly.
  • Integrated the following APIs with conditional logic to display fields and data:
  • g/ab/dashboard/primary_records
  • g/ab/dashboard/primary_records_fields
  • g/ab/dashboard/graph_preview
  • Added a "Result" button and implemented logic to change the button color on mouse hover.
  • Worked on displaying graph data using the new API functionality.
Tasks for 24/10/24
  • Displayed all real-time data in all Apache ECharts graphs.
  • Enabled real-time data display in expanded chart and table functionality.
  • Created a data format for non-functional charts.
  • Fixed the double pop issue.
  • Resolved bubble chart issue.
Tasks for 25/10/24
  • Resolved the KPI edit tile drawer issue.
  • Added modal notifications for Add Tile, Edit Tile, Clone Tile, and Delete Tile actions.
  • Fixed UI issue to display the loader in the center.
  • Completed API integration for global configuration settings.
  • Conducted developer-level testing and bug fixing.
Tasks for 29/10/24
  • Integrated API for default page settings and implemented conditional logic to display the default set page.
  • Completed the integration of the delete page API.
  • Added new fields and UI for stacked charts within all chart types.
data.custrecord_knz_kmcf_assigned_toText: Narayana, Charan, G Ashok, Sreevani, Naganath, Sai Santhosh
